{"title":"矿山，幸福的晚年（外一首）","authors":["韩忆萍"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":9,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿山，幸福的晚年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩忆萍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山下，一座瓜棚小院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪白的胡须雪白的衬衫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山上，一条贴山的管道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑墨描出一根悬空的弓弦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煤涌上井，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山坡下陷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我凝视眼前老矿工的手脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染人的煤粉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漆黑十指。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白发下面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皱褶深陷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消瘦了身体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰满了矿山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美好的回忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将似迤逶的山峦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲得响的青春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安详对弈的晚年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！一根紧绷的弓弦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"系着两个燃点！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头灯房的姑娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排排充好的矿灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑容可掬的姑娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引导矿工的足迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去觅煤层的阳光！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把粒粒美好的种子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"递到矿工的手上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说矿工缺少爱情？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你把那矿工灯拭得雪亮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果那种子是点星星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿工的脚下将涌起无数月亮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果那种子是颗真挚的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请你多采乌金作为爱情的报偿！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}